_Asturias" title="Miguel Angel Asturias — turc" lang="tr" hreflang="tr" class="interlanguage-link-target">Türkçe</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-tt"><a href="https://tt.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9C%D0%B8%D0%B3%D0%B5%D0%BB_%D0%90%D0%BD%D1%85%D0%B5%D0%BB_%D0%90%D1%81%D1%82%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%B0%D1%81" title="Мигел Анхел Астуриас — tatar" lang="tt" hreflang="tt" class="interlanguage-link-target">Татарча/tatarça</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uk"><a href="https://uk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9C%D1%96%D0%B3%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8C_%D0%90%D0%BD%D1%85%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8C_%D0%90%D1%81%D1%82%D1%83%D1%80%D1%96%D0%B0%D1%81" title="Мігель Анхель Астуріас — ukrainien" lang="uk" hreflang="uk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Українська</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ur"><a href="https://ur.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D9%85%DB%8C%DA%AF%D9%88%D8%A6%D9%88%D9%84_%D8%A7%DB%8C%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%84_%D8%A7%D8%B3%D9%B9%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%B3" title="میگوئول اینجل اسٹریس — ourdou" lang="ur" hreflang="ur" class="interlanguage-link-target">اردو</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uz"><a href="https://uz.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_%C3%81ngel_Asturias" title="Miguel Ángel Asturias — ouzbek" lang="uz" hreflang="uz" class="interlanguage-link-target">Oʻzbekcha/ўзбекча</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-vi"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_%C3%81ngel_Asturias" title="Miguel Ángel Asturias — vietnamien" lang="vi" hreflang="vi" class="interlanguage-link-target">Tiếng Việt</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-wuu"><a href="https://wuu.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B1%B3%E6%A0%BC%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E5%AE%89%E8%B5%AB%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%9B%BE%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%9A%E6%96%AF" title="米格尔·安赫尔·阿斯图里亚斯 — wu" lang="wuu" hreflang="wuu" class="interlanguage-link-target">吴语</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-xmf"><a href="https://xmf.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E1%83%9B%E1%83%98%E1%83%92%E1%83%94%E1%83%9A_%E1%83%90%E1%83%A1%E1%83%A2%E1%8