eur australien)">George Miller</a> <small>(<a href="/wiki/Festival_de_Cannes_2016" title="Festival de Cannes 2016">2016</a>)</small></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Pedro_Almod%C3%B3var" title="Pedro Almodóvar">Pedro Almodóvar</a> <small>(<a href="/wiki/Festival_de_Cannes_2017" title="Festival de Cannes 2017">2017</a>)</small></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Cate_Blanchett" title="Cate Blanchett">Cate Blanchett</a> <small>(<a href="/wiki/Festival_de_Cannes_2018" title="Festival de Cannes 2018">2018</a>)</small></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Alejandro_Gonz%C3%A1lez_I%C3%B1%C3%A1rritu" title="Alejandro González Iñárritu">Alejandro González Iñárritu</a> <small>(<a href="/wiki/Festival_de_Cannes_2019" title="Festival de Cannes 2019">2019</a>)</small></span></td>
